## Q. [How to limits the ssh connection]
<u>ANS.</u> 
Edit file (/etc/security/limits.conf)
    #ftp             hard    nproc           0
    #@student        -       maxlogins       4
    tester            -       maxlogins       1
    
** (NOTE: here "root" user not working for ristriction but rest other user is fine.) ** 
(https://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/26170/sshd-config-maxsessions-parameter)
(https://www.cyberciti.biz/faq/linux-unix-osx-bsd-ssh-multiplexing-to-speed-up-ssh-connections/)
